==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: humidify
<hw>humidify</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to render (gases, especially
air) humid or to increase the moisture content of; <as>as, We have a
machine that <ex>humidifies</ex> the air in the house</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> moisturize, make humid, make more humid.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

